[I] Lightweight scanning program

[T] Skanlite is a simple image scanning application to scan and save images. It
[T] is optimized for scanning with flatbed scanners. Skanlite can capture not
[T] only photos and documents, but also transparent slides and filmstrips, with
[T] supported scanners.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/skanlite/

[A] The KDE-Team
[M] Rene Rebe <rene@t2-project.org>

